name: Crypto Campfire IMPACT Coffee Mug
description:
Purchase of this NFT gets you a REAL LIFE physical Crypto Campfire coffee mug!
International shipping is included!

This limited edition (10/10) NFT will mark the LAST TEN MUGS of this design that will ever be sold. Once these NFTs sell out, this design will be discontinued forever!


****** VERY IMPORTANT ******
****************************

How to redeem this NFT for your mug:

The process is very simple AND you get to keep the NFT. 
1. Log into hic et nunc (sync your wallet) and follow this link (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/189648) to get to our "Confirmation Code Generator" Interactive OBJKT. This OBJKT generates a confirmation code unique to the wallet address of the user currently looking at it. That's you ;)

2. Send an email to redeem@cryptocampfirepodcast.com and include your confirmation code, wallet address, and shipping information. 

That's it! Now you have a cool NFT in your wallet and a Crypto Campfire coffee mug on its way :)
